17:26.190 --> 17:27.300
Fikir betul-betul.

17:27.300 --> 17:28.970
Persoalan abad ini.

17:29.470 --> 17:30.500
Ya.

17:30.500 --> 17:31.440
Tidur.

17:48.500 --> 17:50.860
(Yan)

17:51.300 --> 17:52.680
Abang, awak mahu pergi lagi?

